ghtly longer than usual to respond. Otherwise, the best way to get in touch=
 is to drop airmail from a seaplane...<br/><br/>In tonight=E2=80=99s email,=
 a veritable candy bowl of news and notes from across the industry during a=
n uncommonly busy August. I have some fresh reporting on Comcast, Warner Br=
os. Discovery, CBS, ABC, and Axios.<br/><br/><i>But first, a few notes from=
 my partners</i>=E2=80=A6<br/><br/></p><ul style=3D"margin:0;color:#000000;=
