t moves in this Vulcan chess match quite soon. Comcast=E2=80=99s agreements=
 with Zaz=E2=80=99s Discovery cable assets expire next quarter.<br/><br/>Me=
anwhile, as one media executive put it, Comcast executives are now =E2=80=
