cape for carriage fees: =E2=80=9CWhy is TNT $3 per month when USA is 50 cen=
ts or AMC is $1? I=E2=80=99m looking forward to seeing what happens in the =
next year or two. I really am.=E2=80=9D <br/><br/>Comcast is also likely to=
 have additional leverage over WBD due to CNN=E2=80=99s poor viewership=E2=
=80=94the network=E2=80=99s ratings in recent years have reached an all-tim=
e low. And while C.E.O. <b>Mark Thompson </b>is saying all the right things=
